       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. ADD-TO.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 WS-TOTAL   PIC 9(4) VALUE 100.
       01 WS-AMOUNT  PIC 9(4) VALUE 25.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           DISPLAY "Before: " WS-TOTAL
           ADD WS-AMOUNT TO WS-TOTAL
           DISPLAY "After:  " WS-TOTAL
           ADD 50 TO WS-TOTAL
           DISPLAY "Final:  " WS-TOTAL
           STOP RUN.
